      "note": "description",
      "abstract": "Establishes enhanced terms of imprisonment for burglary and theft offenses, which shall apply when the value of the property exceeds certain dollar amounts.  Increase penalties for habitual property crime offenders.  Establishes the selling of stolen property as a theft offense."
